item.title: Awards and Activities
item.description: Awards and Honors 2018-2020 Scholar Athlete: I maintained above a 3.5 GPA for the entire CIF swim season. 2019 Most Improved Varsity Swimmer: Was awarded this by my coach for my dedication to improving throughout the season. 2019 USA Water Polo Academic All-American: Received this award for participating in a national level event while also achieving a 3.6 or higher GPA. OnBoard! Leader: Was chosen by faculty at my school to be a mentor for first year students.
